00:18:51,830 --> 00:18:54,450
我们对你哥哥有多难过
how sad we are about your brother

195
00:18:54,620 --> 00:18:58,750
我们一发现 伊吉尼奥就亲自去告诉你了
As soon as we found out, Higinio himself went to tell you that

196
00:18:59,950 --> 00:19:02,450
现在你明白我为什么要做什么了吗？
Now do you understand why I have to do something?

197
00:19:02,620 --> 00:19:04,250
我求你了
I'm begging you please

198
00:19:06,500 --> 00:19:08,500
你应该对你丈夫说的
You should have said that to your husband

199
00:19:09,450 --> 00:19:10,540
恳求他
Begged him

200
00:19:12,830 --> 00:19:15,040
你应该求他的 对吗？
You should have begged him, right?

201
00:19:17,580 --> 00:19:18,750
来吧 贡萨洛
Come on, Gonzalo

202
00:19:18,910 --> 00:19:21,370
不要拉窗帘 -我要带走他们
Don't take the curtains. - I'm taking them

203
00:19:21,540 --> 00:19:24,080
不要 它们是我的 把窗帘给我
Don't, they're mine. Give me the curtains!

204
00:19:24,330 --> 00:19:25,330
把他们交出来
Hand them over

205
00:19:25,790 --> 00:19:27,790
它们是我的 给我
They're mine, give them to me!

206
00:19:28,660 --> 00:19:30,950
别拿窗帘 贡萨洛
Don't take the curtains, Gonzalo

207
00:19:52,580 --> 00:19:56,540
什么事？搜查雷麦黛丝的房子
What is it? Searching Remedios's house.

208
00:20:21,450 --> 00:20:22,660
“金发男”
”The blond guy”,

209
00:20:22,750 --> 00:20:24,950
和“寨子男”逃走了
and “the stockade guy” got away

210
00:20:42,290 --> 00:20:43,660
你在那里做什么？
What are you doing there?

211
00:20:43,830 --> 00:20:45,750
外面发生了什么？
What's going on outside?

212
00:20:46,290 --> 00:20:48,660
不 这不是重点 我说了什么？
No, that isn't the point. What did I say?

213
00:20:51,540 --> 00:20:52,620
你和谁谈过了吗？
Did you talk to anyone?

214
00:20:53,370 --> 00:20:56,410
帮我个忙 进去吧 -你和谁谈过了吗？
Do me a favour and get in there. - Did you talk to anyone?

215
00:21:08,830 --> 00:21:10,790
阿曼多改变了立场
Armando has switched sides

216
00:21:11,910 --> 00:21:12,950
双胞胎 对吗？
The twin, right?

217
00:21:14,080 --> 00:21:15,500
不 诺加莱斯
No, Nogales

218
00:21:15,660 --> 00:21:16,660
诺加莱斯？
Nogales?

219
00:21:17,330 --> 00:21:18,580
诺加莱斯？
Nogales?

220
00:21:21,450 --> 00:21:23,450
我现在谁都不相信
I don't trust anyone now

221
00:21:25,500 --> 00:21:27,500
贡萨洛正在分发一份名单
Gonzalo is giving out a list of names

222
00:21:32,160 --> 00:21:34,830
没有什么比愤怒的白痴更糟糕的了
There's nothing worse than an angry idiot

223
00:21:35,160 --> 00:21:38,040
黄油在他嘴里不会融化 现在看看他在胡说八道
Butter wouldn't melt in his mouth, now look at him blabbing

224
00:21:39,870 --> 00:21:43,450
他的问题是他害怕
The trouble with him is that he's scared

225
00:21:44,290 --> 00:21:45,540
害怕什么？
Scared of what?

226
00:21:46,700 --> 00:21:47,750
我不知道
I don't know

227
00:21:48,080 --> 00:21:49,500
我们会回来的
That we'll come back

228
00:21:56,080 --> 00:21:57,540
你涂药膏了吗？
Did you put on the ointment?

229
00:21:58,330 --> 00:22:00,540
我完全忘记了药膏
I forgot all about the ointment

230
00:22:03,950 --> 00:22:05,330
小心 小心
Careful, careful

231
00:22:11,870 --> 00:22:13,200
疼吗？
Does it hurt?

232
00:22:14,580 --> 00:22:16,000
我可以忍受
I can put up with it

233
00:22:24,790 --> 00:22:26,790
天啊 你真臭
God, you really stink

234
00:22:27,000 --> 00:22:29,000
你说我臭是什么意思？-这个
What do you mean I stink? - This

235
00:22:29,370 --> 00:22:32,040
怎么了？它有我的味道
What's wrong? It smells of me

236
00:22:32,540 --> 00:22:34,540
自从你进去后就没换过
You haven't changed it since you got in there

237
00:22:34,700 --> 00:22:36,330
我为什么要换衬衫？
Why would I change shirts?

238
00:23:27,700 --> 00:23:31,540
我的背真的很痛
My back is really hurting.

239
00:23:31,700 --> 00:23:34,700
我已经能走路了
I can already walk

240
00:23:43,370 --> 00:23:44,370
伊吉尼奥
Higinio

241
00:23:44,410 --> 00:23:45,410
什么？
What?

242
00:23:47,500 --> 00:23:50,700
下周的计划是不可能的
What was planed for the next week is going to be impossible

243
00:24:00,580 --> 00:24:02,370
你怎么能这么说？
How can you say that?

244
00:24:04,620 --> 00:24:07,870
他们逮捕了要带我们去葡萄牙的人
They arrested the man who was going to get us to Portugal

245
00:24:08,950 --> 00:24:11,370
那不可能 罗莎 那不可能
That can't be, Rosa, that can't be

246
00:24:11,830 --> 00:24:14,830
那不可能 -没关系 我会想办法的
That can't be. - It's all right, I'll find a way

247
00:24:15,660 --> 00:24:18,790
我们现在必须离开 我们必须冒这个险
We have to leave now. We have to risk it

248
00:24:19,200 --> 00:24:21,620
我们不能再等了
We can't wait any longer

249
00:24:22,040 --> 00:24:24,040
现在是时候了
Now is the time

250
00:24:24,330 --> 00:24:26,330
我们现在必须离开 -看在上帝的份上
We must leave now. - For God's sake

251
00:24:28,830 --> 00:24:31,580
放轻松 我会找到办法的
Take it easy, I'll find a way

252
00:24:33,540 --> 00:24:39,290
逮捕——法律权威对自由的暂时丧失
arrest - temporary loss of freedom by authority of law

253
00:24:39,370 --> 00:24:41,370
如果你什么都不知道 为什么这么紧张？
If you don't know anything, why so nervous?

254
00:24:41,660 --> 00:24:42,910
我不知道
I don't know

255
00:24:43,160 --> 00:24:46,000
如果你这么晚来我家 你会有什么期待？
What do you expect if you come to my house this late?

256
00:24:48,700 --> 00:24:51,580
你没听说过他 甚至没从别人那里听说过？
You didn't hear about him, not even from someone else?

257
00:24:51,750 --> 00:24:55,830
不 我已经说过了 他走了 这是我最后一次听到
No, I already said I didn't. He left and that was the last I heard

258
00:24:56,620 --> 00:25:00,160
那你为什么这么想把他从名单上抹去？
Then why are you so desperate to have him wiped off the list?

259
00:25:01,500 --> 00:25:04,000
你还没喝够吗？
Haven't you already had enough?

260
00:25:04,870 --> 00:25:06,000
我什么都不知道
I don't know anything

261
00:25:06,250 --> 00:25:07,790
他离开时你说了什么？
What did you say when he left?

262
00:25:07,950 --> 00:25:10,290
没什么 我甚至不能说再见
Nothing, I couldn't even say goodbye

263
00:25:10,450 --> 00:25:12,080
你怎么知道他什么时候离开的？
So how did you know what time he left?

264
00:25:12,290 --> 00:25:13,580
时间 我
The time, I

265
00:25:13,750 --> 00:25:17,410
他早上离开了 但不知道什么时候
He left in the morning, but I don't know at what time

266
00:25:20,000 --> 00:25:23,580
前几天他们看见你在洗一个男人的衬衫
They saw you washing a man's shirt the other day

267
00:25:27,500 --> 00:25:28,580
不要装傻
Don't act stupid

268
00:25:29,080 --> 00:25:30,620
这里没有什么不被注意的
Nothing goes unnoticed here

269
00:25:31,160 --> 00:25:32,950
还是不是你丈夫的？
Or wasn't it your husband's?

270
00:25:33,160 --> 00:25:36,450
是的 它是...这是我丈夫的 但是
Yes, it is... It was my husband's, but

271
00:25:37,500 --> 00:25:41,950
他走后一周 我发现它很脏 所以我就把它洗了
I found it a week after he left, it was dirty so I washed it

272
00:25:48,370 --> 00:25:52,330
你的邻居说你总是开着前门
Your neighbors say you always kept the front door open,

273
00:25:52,830 --> 00:25:54,790
现在它几乎总是关着
now it's almost always shut

274
00:26:00,080 --> 00:26:01,660
正是我所需要的
Just what I needed

275
00:26:02,080 --> 00:26:03,540
别哭了
Quit crying

276
00:26:04,250 --> 00:26:05,950
我说别哭了 好吗？
I said quit crying, okay?

277
00:26:07,000 --> 00:26:10,080
如果你现在不合作 我们有命令要执行
If you don't collaborate now, we have orders to carry out

278
00:26:10,290 --> 00:26:12,540
你瞧...我真的什么都不知道
You see... I really don't know anything

279
00:26:13,250 --> 00:26:14,500
几个问题
A couple of questions

280
00:26:14,620 --> 00:26:17,200
不不不还有问题吗？但是我已经告诉你了
No, no, no, more questions? But I already told you

281
00:26:17,370 --> 00:26:19,790
不求你了 -不要让它变得更难
No, please! - Don't make it more difficult

282
00:26:19,950 --> 00:26:21,330
请不要这样做
Please don't do this!

283
00:26:21,500 --> 00:26:25,580
我什么都不知道 也不知道他在哪里 看在上帝的份上 请不要
I don't know anything or where he is. For God's sake, please don't!

284
00:26:25,750 --> 00:26:27,500
来吧 -我想留在这里
Come on now. - I want to stay here!

285
00:26:27,660 --> 00:26:30,250
我告诉你我什么都不知道
I'm telling you that I don't know anything!

286
00:26:30,870 --> 00:26:32,500
请
Please

287
00:27:05,950 --> 00:27:06,950
他不在吗？
Is he not here?

288
00:27:07,160 --> 00:27:08,370
看起来是这样
Looks that way

289
00:27:08,620 --> 00:27:10,700
我告诉你 我听到噪音 嗯？
I tell you, I hear noises, huh?

290
00:27:12,660 --> 00:27:14,330
你检查过了吗？-哪里？
Did you check there? - Where?

291
00:27:14,580 --> 00:27:15,790
在那里
There

292
00:27:16,080 --> 00:27:17,500
罐子在哪里
Where the jars are

293
00:27:18,910 --> 00:27:20,250
看看里面
Have a look inside

294
00:27:26,250 --> 00:27:27,620
它是空的
It's empty

295
00:27:33,910 --> 00:27:35,830
看起来这里面有点油
Looks like there's a bit of oil in this one

296
00:27:36,290 --> 00:27:37,540
确定吗？
Sure?

297
00:27:50,660 --> 00:27:52,700
这里没人 -没什么？
No one here. - Nothing?

298
00:29:12,450 --> 00:29:13,750
滚开
Scram!

299
00:29:17,330 --> 00:29:18,330
滚开
Scram!

300
00:29:18,410 --> 00:29:20,410
滚开 那不是给你的
Scram, that isn't for you!

301
00:29:26,830 --> 00:29:28,500
给我
Give it to me!

302
00:30:13,910 --> 00:30:15,160
罗莎
Rosa

303
00:30:23,160 --> 00:30:24,290
罗莎
Rosa

304
00:30:31,540 --> 00:30:33,450
他们对你做了什么？
What did they do to you?

305
00:30:34,580 --> 00:30:35,910
发生什么事了？
What happened?

306
00:30:41,910 --> 00:30:43,160
发生什么事了？
What happened?

307
00:30:53,250 --> 00:30:54,620
你怎么了？
What happened to you?

308
00:30:59,160 --> 00:31:02,290
他们告诉我他们抓到你了
They told me that they'd caught you

309
00:31:03,450 --> 00:31:05,080
我一句话也没说
I didn't say a word

310
00:31:15,160 --> 00:31:17,580
结束了 让他们抓住我
It's over. Let them just catch me

311
00:31:25,700 --> 00:31:28,040
如果我连你都照顾不了 为什么我会在这里？
Why am I here if I can't even take care of you?

312
00:31:58,250 --> 00:31:59,410
来这里
Come here

313
00:33:21,290 --> 00:33:22,330
伊吉尼奥
Higinio

314
00:33:23,330 --> 00:33:24,370
什么？
What?

315
00:33:26,450 --> 00:33:30,950
他们告诉我 我必须每天去军营报到
They told me I have to report to the barracks every day

316
00:33:32,660 --> 00:33:33,750
和
And

317
00:33:34,580 --> 00:33:37,370
他们让我把门开着
They've made me leave the front door open

318
00:33:40,500 --> 00:33:41,830
没关系
It's all right

319
00:33:42,750 --> 00:33:43,790
没关系
It's fine

320
00:33:43,950 --> 00:33:46,660
答应我 如果我不在 你不会出来
Promise me you won't come out if I'm not here

321
00:33:47,660 --> 00:33:48,950
答应我
Promise me

322
00:33:50,830 --> 00:33:51,950
发誓
Swear on it

323
00:33:52,370 --> 00:33:53,450
我发誓
I swear

324
00:34:11,540 --> 00:34:13,700
你想象大海是什么样子的？
What do you imagine the sea looks like?

325
00:34:15,500 --> 00:34:16,500
我不知道
I don't know

326
00:34:16,580 --> 00:34:17,660
贡萨洛来了
Gonzalo is coming.

327
00:34:17,790 --> 00:34:21,200
我想象当阳光猛烈照射下来时
I imagine that when the sunlight is shining down hard

328
00:34:21,290 --> 00:34:22,290
我想你
I miss you.

329
00:34:22,410 --> 00:34:25,450
它一定像夏天的乡村
it must be like the countryside in summer

330
00:34:25,910 --> 00:34:27,830
太阳与地平线融为一体
and the sun merges with the horizon

331
00:34:29,160 --> 00:34:31,160
就像那样 但是有水
Like that, but with water

332
00:34:32,910 --> 00:34:34,330
先别走
Don't go yet.

333
00:34:34,450 --> 00:34:35,580
真遗憾
What a pity

334
00:34:35,950 --> 00:34:36,950
我爱你
I love you.

335
00:34:37,200 --> 00:34:40,660
我们应该让你父亲支付蜜月费用
We should have let your father pay for the honeymoon

336
00:34:42,500 --> 00:34:45,950
当我们用挣来的钱去做的时候 我们会更享受它
We'll enjoy it more when we do it with the money we earn

337
00:34:46,790 --> 00:34:49,160
你知道今天是星期几吗？
Do you know what day today is?

338
00:34:49,620 --> 00:34:51,540
当然 周年快乐
Of course, happy anniversary.

339
00:34:56,660 --> 00:34:57,790
罗莎
Rosa

340
00:34:58,250 --> 00:35:01,290
以后别忘了适当搅拌骨灰
Don't forget to stir the ashes properly later

341
00:35:02,750 --> 00:35:03,870
好
All right

342
00:35:04,580 --> 00:35:06,580
你已经告诉我三次了
You told me three times already

343
00:35:10,910 --> 00:35:13,250
我向你要的书呢？
What about the books I asked you for?

344
00:35:14,830 --> 00:35:17,910
我不能被看到带着关于政治的书
I can't be seen bringing books on politics

345
00:35:18,040 --> 00:35:21,040
还有那些...很明显他们不适合我
and things that... It's obvious they're not for me

346
00:35:30,370 --> 00:35:33,500
孩子们 过来 你好 -你好
Kids, come here. Hello. - Hello

347
00:35:37,950 --> 00:35:39,290
你在做什么?
What are you doing?

348
00:35:46,370 --> 00:35:48,370
帮我个忙 进去吧
Do me a favour and get in there

349
00:35:53,040 --> 00:35:55,700
你能进去吗？
Can you please get in there?

350
00:35:56,080 --> 00:35:58,620
我在听人们在说什么
I'm listening to what people are saying

351
00:36:00,830 --> 00:36:03,450
我透过窗户偷看的时候看见了佩罗
I saw Pero when I was peeking through the window

352
00:36:05,080 --> 00:36:07,120
他不是站在民族主义阵营的前线吗？
Wasn't he on the front with the Nationalist faction?

353
00:36:10,200 --> 00:36:13,540
要么他有一个双胞胎兄弟 要么他在外面庆祝胜利
Either he has a twin brother or he's out there celebrating the victory

354
00:36:25,040 --> 00:36:26,080
罗莎
Rosa

355
00:36:30,040 --> 00:36:31,660
结束了吗？
Is it over?

356
00:36:41,620 --> 00:36:43,200
你为什么不告诉我？
So why don't you tell me?

357
00:36:43,580 --> 00:36:45,290
因为还没有结束
Because it isn't over

358
00:36:50,580 --> 00:36:52,580
他们处决了阿里纳斯
They executed Arenas

359
00:36:54,700 --> 00:36:57,910
恩里克 安德烈斯 奎约
And Enrique, Andrés, Quijo

360
00:36:58,580 --> 00:37:02,250
他们杀了所有被抓的议员
They killed all the councillors that they caught

361
00:37:04,250 --> 00:37:06,450
他们已经悬赏捉拿你
They've put out a reward for your capture

362
00:37:10,790 --> 00:37:13,370
我听说他们出价6万比塞塔
I heard they're offering 60,000 pesetas

363
00:37:15,450 --> 00:37:17,370
我做了什么才值那么多钱？
What have I done to be worth that much?

364
00:37:17,540 --> 00:37:20,330
我不知道 他们说你做了可怕的事情
I don't know, they're saying you did terrible things

365
00:37:22,330 --> 00:37:24,950
谁说的？-每个人
Who's saying that? - Everyone

366
00:37:26,370 --> 00:37:28,410
那些从前面回来的人
Those coming back from the front

367
00:37:28,580 --> 00:37:31,000
他们责怪你们中没有回来的人
they are blaming those of you who didn't come back

368
00:37:33,750 --> 00:37:35,750
所以 还没有结束
So, it isn't over

369
00:37:49,790 --> 00:37:56,750
危险——可能发生坏事的风险或迫在眉睫的可能性
danger - risk or imminent possibility that something bad may occur

370
00:38:07,370 --> 00:38:08,910
你觉得她知道些什么吗？
Think she knows something?

371
00:38:09,660 --> 00:38:12,450
我也这么认为她在隐瞒什么
I think so. She's hiding something

372
00:38:13,200 --> 00:38:15,870
我们必须审问她 尽我们所能
We have to interrogate her, get as much as we can

373
00:38:16,370 --> 00:38:19,330
在这里审问她 -我不同意
Interrogate her right here. - I don't agree

374
00:38:19,450 --> 00:38:22,410
我们带她一起去吧 审问她和其他什么
Let's take her with us. Interrogate her and whatever else

375
00:38:28,500 --> 00:38:30,080
不 不可能 听我说
No, no way. Listen to me

376
00:38:30,540 --> 00:38:32,750
我们照我说的做 在这里审问她
We do as I say, interrogate her here

377
00:38:58,750 --> 00:39:00,000
你在大喊大叫
You're shouting

378
00:39:10,160 --> 00:39:12,500
会再发生的 等着瞧吧
It'll happen again, just wait and see

379
00:39:13,410 --> 00:39:16,620
自从战争结束后 他变得更加着迷
Since the war ended he's become even more obsessed

380
00:39:19,000 --> 00:39:20,000
罗莎
Rosa!

381
00:39:20,080 --> 00:39:24,450
贡萨洛 我是伊吉尼奥 我的岳父 我们在吃饭 好吗？
Gonzalo, It’s Higinio, my father-in-law. We are having dinner, okay?

382
00:39:24,750 --> 00:39:25,540
行
Okay

383
00:39:25,620 --> 00:39:27,790
每天都一样
Same thing every day

384
00:39:30,830 --> 00:39:33,370
那么 伊吉尼奥没事吧？
So, is Higinio all right?

385
00:39:36,410 --> 00:39:37,660
他没事
He's all right

386
00:39:38,580 --> 00:39:40,950
但是这越来越让人无法忍受了
But this is getting unbearable

387
00:39:41,830 --> 00:39:44,290
他开始在睡梦中大喊大叫
He's beginning to shout in his sleep

388
00:39:44,540 --> 00:39:47,660
前几天他们把这个地方翻了个底朝天
They turned the place upside down the other day

389
00:39:47,830 --> 00:39:49,830
我不知道他们怎么没找到他
I don't know how they didn't find him

390
00:39:52,500 --> 00:39:53,870
你是说他在这里？
You mean he's here?

391
00:39:58,540 --> 00:39:59,540
他在那里
He's there

392
00:40:00,160 --> 00:40:01,660
罐子下面
Under the jars

393
00:40:02,750 --> 00:40:04,950
他藏在里面
He's hiding inside there

394
00:40:09,370 --> 00:40:10,660
亲爱的上帝
Dear God

395
00:40:13,910 --> 00:40:16,330
他在那里已经三年了
He's been there three years

396
00:40:17,450 --> 00:40:18,500
几乎
Pretty much

397
00:40:20,120 --> 00:40:24,200
如果你愿意 把架子上的盘子拿来 说几句话
If you want, fetch the plates on the shelf and have a word

398
00:40:24,790 --> 00:40:28,120
请帮我把那些盘子拿来
Do me a favour and fetch me those plates, please

399
00:40:33,290 --> 00:40:34,330
父亲
Father

400
00:40:36,250 --> 00:40:38,790
从架子上拿些东西 任何东西
Pick something off the shelf, anything

401
00:40:41,700 --> 00:40:44,080
但是你为什么不跟我说点什么？
But why didn't you say anything to me?

402
00:40:44,250 --> 00:40:46,750
我们认为最好不要告诉任何人
We thought it was best not to tell anyone

403
00:40:46,870 --> 00:40:48,330
父亲 我需要你的帮助
Father, I need your help

404
00:40:48,620 --> 00:40:49,700
你想要什么都行
Whatever you want

405
00:40:50,910 --> 00:40:53,000
餐具柜所在的墙
The wall where the sideboard is

406
00:40:53,290 --> 00:40:55,500
我需要你建一堵假墙
I need you to build a false wall,

407
00:40:55,580 --> 00:40:58,500
然后在餐具柜后面挖一个洞
and then make a hole behind the sideboard

408
00:40:58,620 --> 00:41:00,910
你想藏在那里吗？
You want to hide in there?

409
00:41:01,160 --> 00:41:02,200
是
Yes

410
00:41:03,330 --> 00:41:04,750
你的房子更安全
Your house is safer

411
00:41:04,910 --> 00:41:06,370
罗莎会给你看计划
Rosa will show you the plans

412
00:41:19,660 --> 00:41:21,870
你建墙越快越好
The sooner you build the wall, the better

413
00:41:22,910 --> 00:41:25,830
一旦准备好了 伊吉尼奥就会去那里
As soon as it's ready, Higinio will go there

414
00:41:27,750 --> 00:41:28,870
你呢？
What about you?

415
00:41:30,700 --> 00:41:33,000
i...如果你不介意的话
I... If you don't mind,

416
00:41:33,410 --> 00:41:35,080
我会和你一起住
I'd move in with you

417
00:41:35,660 --> 00:41:39,660
如果人们问 我们会告诉他们钱很紧
If people ask, we tell them that money is really tight and

418
00:41:39,950 --> 00:41:42,950
这样我就可以管理你已故妻子的工作室
that way I can take charge of your deceased wife's workshop

419
00:41:50,290 --> 00:41:51,410
快
Quick

420
00:41:52,000 --> 00:41:56,370
记得用茴香和熏衣草来清理这个洞以去除气味
Remember to clean the hole with anise and lavender to get rid of the smell

421
00:41:56,540 --> 00:41:57,540
行
Okay

422
00:41:57,660 --> 00:42:00,450
不 等等 等等 让我看看
No, hang on. Wait. Let's see

423
00:42:02,620 --> 00:42:03,750
好了
Done

424
00:42:05,330 --> 00:42:06,580
就这样
That's it

425
00:42:07,830 --> 00:42:09,000
就这样
That's it

426
00:42:09,580 --> 00:42:10,750
准备
Ready

427
00:42:14,750 --> 00:42:16,750
你会做得很好的 又好又快
You'll do a good job. Nice and quick

428
00:42:16,950 --> 00:42:18,250
走吧 你走吧
Go on, off you go

429
00:42:19,080 --> 00:42:19,750
罗莎
Rosa

430
00:42:19,910 --> 00:42:23,120
趁大家都在游行的时候 现在就做 快点
Do it now while everyone is at the procession, hurry

431
00:42:34,830 --> 00:42:35,910
什么事？
What is it?

432
00:42:39,200 --> 00:42:40,370
我不能 -是的 你可以
I can't. - Yes you can

433
00:42:40,540 --> 00:42:42,000
什么意思?听我说
What do you mean? Listen to me

434
00:42:42,160 --> 00:42:44,000
如果你留下来 他们会抓住你的
If you stay, they'll catch you

435
00:42:45,370 --> 00:42:46,830
你现在必须走了
You have to go now

436
00:42:48,450 --> 00:42:50,120
你当然可以 你为什么不呢？
Of course you can. Why wouldn't you?

437
00:42:50,290 --> 00:42:51,370
你能做到的
You can do it

438
00:42:51,540 --> 00:42:53,370
我不会丢下你不管的
I won't leave you alone

439
00:42:53,700 --> 00:42:55,500
你会做得很好的 好吗？
You'll do a great job, okay?

440
00:42:56,950 --> 00:42:58,200
开始
Come on

441
00:42:59,200 --> 00:43:03,040
西班牙万岁
REDS OUT LONG LIVE SPAIN

442
00:43:07,500 --> 00:43:08,540
匆忙
Hurry

443
00:43:27,040 --> 00:43:28,660
快点 我们要迟到了
Come on, we'll be late

444
00:43:28,910 --> 00:43:30,040
移动它
Move it

445
00:44:19,790 --> 00:44:21,910
你在找什么吗 夫人？
Are you looking for something, madam?

446
00:44:22,450 --> 00:44:23,450
不好意思
Excuse me!

447
00:44:24,790 --> 00:44:26,080
不好意思
Excuse me!

448
00:44:31,540 --> 00:44:33,450
站住 这是国民警卫队
Halt, this is the Civil Guard!

449
00:44:34,910 --> 00:44:36,200
住手 否则我开枪了
Stop or I'll shoot!

450
00:44:39,830 --> 00:44:41,450
这是国民警卫队
This is the Civil Guard!

451
00:46:31,450 --> 00:46:32,620
进来
Come in

452
00:46:34,700 --> 00:46:36,160
脱下那些衣服
Take off those clothes

453
00:46:38,290 --> 00:46:39,450
他们全部
All of them

454
00:46:41,790 --> 00:46:43,370
你为什么花了这么长时间？
Why did you take so long?

455
00:46:43,540 --> 00:46:45,000
我迷路了
I got lost

456
00:46:46,160 --> 00:46:47,750
在你的村子里？-是的
In your village? - Yes

457
00:46:49,370 --> 00:46:51,620
里面有一个洗脸盆可以自己洗
There's a basin in there to wash yourself

458
00:46:52,450 --> 00:46:53,700
快点 快点
Come on, hurry up

459
00:47:30,330 --> 00:47:31,540
儿子
Son

460
00:47:31,700 --> 00:47:33,080
你还好吗？
Are you all right?

461
00:47:34,120 --> 00:47:34,910
是
Yes

462
00:47:35,080 --> 00:47:37,080
你需要什么吗？
Do you need anything?

463
00:47:37,580 --> 00:47:38,250
不
No

464
00:47:38,410 --> 00:47:40,750
如果你需要什么...-安静
If you need anything... - Silence!

465
00:47:42,620 --> 00:47:43,870
沉默
Silence

466
00:47:44,700 --> 00:47:46,160
这正是我需要的
That's what I need

467
00:48:00,370 --> 00:48:07,370
将人或动物放在他们不能离开的地方
enclose - put a person or an animal in a place they cannot leave

468
00:48:08,750 --> 00:48:11,910
我在兵营旁边的广场上看见了他
I saw him in the square, next to the barracks

469
00:48:13,750 --> 00:48:16,330
他难过得无法和儿子说再见
So sad he couldn't say goodbye to his son

470
00:48:16,540 --> 00:48:19,200
现在他离开了这个世界 再也不能
Now he's left this world and won't be able to

471
00:48:55,910 --> 00:48:57,910
让我们上路吧
Let's be on our way

472
00:49:40,790 --> 00:49:42,790
1944年2月8日
FEBRUARY 8th, 1944

473
00:50:30,450 --> 00:50:32,410
我有三袋土 你知道吗？
I have three sacks of dirt, you know?

474
00:50:33,500 --> 00:50:35,000
明天给我
Give them to me tomorrow

475
00:50:38,370 --> 00:50:41,370
我估计大约一年后
I reckon that in about a year or so

476
00:50:42,540 --> 00:50:45,660
我会一直挖到树林
I'll have dug the hole as far as the grove

477
00:50:46,870 --> 00:50:48,290
如果发生了什么
And if anything happens

478
00:50:50,750 --> 00:50:52,160
伊吉尼奥 我想要个孩子
Higinio, I want a baby

479
00:50:58,540 --> 00:51:00,080
别再这样了 罗莎
Not this again, Rosa

480
00:51:01,080 --> 00:51:03,080
我们不是说过盟军何时赢得战争吗？
Didn't we say when the allies won the war?

481
00:51:06,000 --> 00:51:08,080
那会是什么时候？他们什么时候会赢？
And when will that be? When will they win?

482
00:51:09,080 --> 00:51:11,250
当我不能再有孩子的时候？
When I can't have children anymore?

483
00:51:13,200 --> 00:51:15,790
当我的肚子开始露出来时 我会去格拉纳达
When my belly starts showing, I'll go to Granada

484
00:51:15,870 --> 00:51:18,620
那我就说这是我必须照顾的侄子
Then I'll say it's a nephew I have to take care of

485
00:51:20,790 --> 00:51:22,500
同时 我如何生存？
Meanwhile, how do I survive?

486
00:51:23,370 --> 00:51:26,410
我会给你留下食物和你需要的任何东西
I'll leave you food and whatever else you need

487
00:51:27,950 --> 00:51:29,370
你能听到自己吗？
Can you hear yourself?

488
00:51:30,250 --> 00:51:33,540
你没意识到这很荒谬而且很危险吗？
Don't you realise it's absurd and really dangerous?

489
00:51:35,370 --> 00:51:38,540
你知道他们会杀了你、我和孩子吗？
Do you realise they could kill you, me and the baby?

490
00:51:38,660 --> 00:51:40,250
你知道会发生什么吗？
Do you realise what might happen?

491
00:51:40,750 --> 00:51:44,120
让我们开动脑筋 是拯救的时候了
Let's use our heads. Is the time to save

492
00:51:44,870 --> 00:51:49,040
我可以帮你织补 做褶边...拜托 罗莎
I can lend you a hand darning, doing hems... Please, Rosa

493
00:51:49,330 --> 00:51:50,870
让我们用我们的头脑
Let's use our heads

494
00:51:52,120 --> 00:51:53,950
让我们给盟友一些时间
Let's give the allies some time

495
00:52:06,290 --> 00:52:09,370
今天 1944年6月6日
Today, 6 June 1944,

496
00:52:09,500 --> 00:52:14,700
盟军已经开始让超过15万名士兵登陆
the allies have started disembarking over 150,000 troops

497
00:52:15,080 --> 00:52:18,410
由艾森豪威尔将军率领的盟军
Led by General Eisenhower, allied troops

498
00:52:18,700 --> 00:52:22,500
战胜了元帅·隆美尔开发的防御系统
have overcome the defences developed by Field Marshal Rommel

499
00:52:23,000 --> 00:52:25,370
英美空军司令部
British and US command of the air

500
00:52:25,540 --> 00:52:27,700
是手术成功的关键
were key to the success of the operation

501
00:52:27,950 --> 00:52:33,000
盟军飞机摧毁了塞纳河和卢瓦尔河上的桥梁
Allied aircraft have destroyed bridges over the Seine and the Loire

502
00:52:33,660 --> 00:52:38,080
成功的登陆使盟军快速前进
The successful landing has enabled allied troops to quickly advance

503
00:52:38,160 --> 00:52:40,040
走向法国的心脏
towards the heart of France

504
00:52:49,000 --> 00:52:50,410
伸出你的手臂
Hold your arms out

505
00:52:51,410 --> 00:52:52,540
好的
Great

506
00:52:53,200 --> 00:52:55,700
看起来不错吧 -是的 你现在会穿它吗？
Looks good, huh? - Yes. Will you wear it now?

507
00:52:56,540 --> 00:52:57,950
我会像那样扣上扣子
I'll button it up like that

508
00:52:58,370 --> 00:52:59,660
这
This

509
00:53:00,200 --> 00:53:03,160
周四之前我会有另一个
I'll have the other one by Thursday

510
00:53:03,950 --> 00:53:05,200
好吗？
Okay?

511
00:53:06,830 --> 00:53:08,080
好的
Great

512
00:53:08,750 --> 00:53:09,950
好
All right

513
00:53:16,160 --> 00:53:17,200
你是艺术家罗莎
You're an artist Rosa

514
00:53:17,750 --> 00:53:21,750
现在你可以告诉人们我不只是缝制服 我修补各种
Now you can tell people I don't just sew uniforms. I mend all sorts

515
00:53:21,830 --> 00:53:23,160
价格也不错
And for a good price, too

516
00:53:23,700 --> 00:53:26,040
他们可以看到最漂亮的女裁缝
And they get to see the prettiest seamstress

517
00:53:26,790 --> 00:53:29,160
你是个圆滑的人 我也向你收费
You're a smooth one. I'm charging you the same

518
00:53:29,290 --> 00:53:32,040
我只是作为一个艺术爱好者说的
I'm just saying it as an art lover

519
00:53:32,450 --> 00:53:33,830
我的靴子在哪里？
Where are my boots?

520
00:53:35,700 --> 00:53:36,950
哦 是的
Oh, yes

521
00:54:26,700 --> 00:54:27,790
停止
Stop

522
00:54:31,410 --> 00:54:32,620
不 停下
No, stop

523
00:54:33,450 --> 00:54:35,290
现在不行 停下
Not now, stop

524
00:54:36,080 --> 00:54:38,370
我得去月经了 停下
I have to get my period, stop

525
00:55:22,330 --> 00:55:24,620
一个来自科尔多瓦的有趣女孩
A fun girl from Córdoba

526
00:55:24,830 --> 00:55:27,450
这让我爱上了她
It's what made me fall in love with her

527
00:55:28,700 --> 00:55:30,290
那时情况不同
Things were different then

528
00:55:31,660 --> 00:55:34,500
因为几个月来
Because for a few months now,

529
00:55:36,250 --> 00:55:37,910
她看起来总是很悲伤
she always looks sad

530
00:55:38,830 --> 00:55:40,540
好像她对什么都不感兴趣
Like she's not excited about anything

531
00:55:42,290 --> 00:55:43,790
现在她所做的就是吃东西
Now all she does is eat

532
00:55:44,750 --> 00:55:46,950
她只吃东西 从不出门
All she does is eat, never leaves the house

533
00:55:47,120 --> 00:55:52,000
我说 卡门 让我们去节日 让你自己漂亮
I say, Carmen, let's go to the festival, make yourself pretty

534
00:55:52,410 --> 00:55:54,330
让我们穿上色彩鲜艳的衣服...
A colourful dress, let's...

535
00:55:54,910 --> 00:55:57,910
充分利用节日 -像以前一样
Make the most of the festival. - Like before

536
00:55:58,620 --> 00:56:00,160
她觉得不能胜任
She doesn't feel up to it

537
00:56:00,700 --> 00:56:01,950
她现在不一样了
She's not the same now

538
00:56:02,120 --> 00:56:03,450
可怜的东西
Poor thing

539
00:56:06,330 --> 00:56:09,000
也许我匆忙结婚了
Maybe I rushed into getting married

540
00:56:11,410 --> 00:56:13,370
别这么说 罗德里戈
Don't say that, Rodrigo

541
00:56:14,250 --> 00:56:18,660
这些事情需要时间 需要习惯
These things take time, they take getting used to

542
00:56:21,080 --> 00:56:22,410
为什么是那张脸？
Why that face?

543
00:56:22,870 --> 00:56:24,040
什么脸？
What face?

544
00:56:24,950 --> 00:56:26,040
那张脸
That face

545
00:56:26,750 --> 00:56:27,790
什么脸？
What face?

546
00:56:29,120 --> 00:56:30,500
你笑了 不是吗？
You smiled, didn't you?

547
00:56:34,370 --> 00:56:36,500
看到我充满疑虑 你觉得好笑吗？
Do you find it funny to see me full of doubts?

548
00:56:37,450 --> 00:56:39,160
不 反过来
No, it's the other way around

549
00:56:39,410 --> 00:56:41,790
我为你们俩感到难过
I feel sad for both of you

550
00:56:43,040 --> 00:56:44,500
不管怎样 我不知道
Anyway, I don't know

551
00:56:45,950 --> 00:56:48,160
这里还有一个洞
There's another hole here, too

552
00:56:48,910 --> 00:56:50,540
又一个？-是的
Another one? - Yes

553
00:56:55,200 --> 00:56:56,660
我没见过那个
I hadn't seen that one

554
00:57:04,080 --> 00:57:05,790
那是星期天的
That's from Sunday

555
00:57:05,870 --> 00:57:10,040
我会帮你修好的 我会把它盖住 这样你就看不见了
I'll mend that for you. I'll cover it up so you won't see it

556
00:57:19,040 --> 00:57:21,040
我知道你和我有同样的感觉
I know you feel the same way as I do

557
00:57:22,910 --> 00:57:24,330
什么意思？
How do you mean?

558
00:57:29,200 --> 00:57:30,910
停下 停下
Stop, stop

559
00:57:32,000 --> 00:57:33,700
我说停下
I said stop!

560
00:57:34,080 --> 00:57:35,120
罗莎
Rosa

561
00:57:35,950 --> 00:57:38,120
马上滚出我的房子
Get out of my house right now

562
00:57:40,290 --> 00:57:43,500
我告诉过你马上出去 否则我会开始尖叫
I told you to get out right now or I'll start screaming

563
00:57:43,620 --> 00:57:44,700
松懈
Take it easy

564
00:57:47,620 --> 00:57:48,700
我要走了
I'm leaving

565
00:57:58,450 --> 00:57:59,660
懦夫
Coward

566
00:58:02,620 --> 00:58:03,950
这是可耻的
It's shameful

567
00:58:06,250 --> 00:58:07,750
这是可耻的
It's shameful

568
00:58:15,790 --> 00:58:16,790
懦夫
Coward

569
00:58:19,330 --> 00:58:21,160
真的 这是可耻的
Really, it's shameful

570
00:58:25,870 --> 00:58:28,000
你以为我不知道你在那里吗
Do you think I don't know you're there

571
00:58:28,500 --> 00:58:29,950
看吗？
watching?

572
00:58:33,250 --> 00:58:34,660
你看到了 对吧？
You saw it, right?

573
00:58:39,410 --> 00:58:40,910
我在和你说话
I'm talking to you

574
