01:18:48,540 --> 01:18:51,080
在信箱里放一份报纸 任何人都可以
pop a newspaper in the letter box, any one will do

766
01:18:51,950 --> 01:18:53,790
也许我会知道发生了什么
Maybe I'll find out what's going on

767
01:18:55,950 --> 01:18:56,950
好吗？
All right?

768
01:18:59,200 --> 01:19:00,200
好吗？
All right?

769
01:19:00,290 --> 01:19:01,700
好吧 -好吧
All right. - All right

770
01:19:13,700 --> 01:19:14,790
明显
Obviously

771
01:19:14,950 --> 01:19:18,000
犯了错误 否则我们就不会处于这种情况
mistakes were made or else we wouldn't be in this situation

772
01:19:18,200 --> 01:19:21,000
但是在共和党时期做了一些好事
But some good things were done in the Republican period

773
01:19:21,450 --> 01:19:24,500
例如 立法重新分配土地
For example, legislating for land redistribution,

774
01:19:24,660 --> 01:19:27,040
教人们读写 医疗保健
teaching people to read and write, healthcare,

775
01:19:27,450 --> 01:19:30,370
确保每个人都能得到治疗
making sure everyone has access to medical treatment

776
01:19:30,540 --> 01:19:31,950
这是人权问题
It's a human rights matter

777
01:19:32,080 --> 01:19:34,950
这一切都可以实现
That can all be achieved

778
01:19:35,120 --> 01:19:37,750
人们应该有体面的生活
People should have a decent living

779
01:19:38,750 --> 01:19:39,910
你不这样认为吗？
Don't you think so?

780
01:19:40,620 --> 01:19:43,250
我不参与那些事情
I don't get involved in those sort of things

781
01:19:44,750 --> 01:19:46,000
政治和我
Politics and me

782
01:19:46,830 --> 01:19:47,830
没有任何东西
Nothing

783
01:19:51,410 --> 01:19:53,410
这就是该政权所取得的成就
That's what the regime has achieved

784
01:19:54,750 --> 01:19:56,370
确保人们不会思考
Ensuring people don't think

785
01:20:01,870 --> 01:20:03,870
想象你所说的发生了
Imagine that what you say happens,

786
01:20:04,040 --> 01:20:07,290
盟军赢得了战争 他们将佛朗哥赶下台
the Allies win the War and they oust Franco from power

787
01:20:08,000 --> 01:20:09,040
你会怎么做？
What would you do?

788
01:20:11,330 --> 01:20:12,330
熄灭
Go out

789
01:20:12,500 --> 01:20:14,080
在街上庆祝
Out on the street to celebrate

790
01:20:15,660 --> 01:20:16,750
像这样？
Like that?

791
01:20:16,910 --> 01:20:18,000
就这样？
Just like that?

792
01:20:18,200 --> 01:20:19,620
这还不够吗？
Isn't that enough?

793
01:20:20,200 --> 01:20:22,080
继续为我所说的而奋斗
And keep on fighting for what I said

794
01:20:28,500 --> 01:20:30,500
你能告诉每个人我是什么吗？
And will you tell everyone what I am?

795
01:20:32,500 --> 01:20:33,950
我是一个守信的人
I'm a man of my word

796
01:20:37,620 --> 01:20:39,950
但你还是会拉长着脸看着我
But you'd still look at me with a long face

797
01:20:40,660 --> 01:20:43,000
盟军不会改变这一点
The Allies won't change that

798
01:20:44,250 --> 01:20:45,290
或者其他人
Or anyone else

799
01:20:46,120 --> 01:20:48,660
我不能改变的是你脑子里在想什么
What I can't change is what goes on in your head

800
01:20:49,790 --> 01:20:50,910
我认为是我的事
What I think is my business

801
01:20:55,410 --> 01:20:56,410
行
Okay

802
01:20:56,910 --> 01:20:58,200
我告诉你一件事
I'll tell you one thing

803
01:20:58,370 --> 01:21:01,040
你妈妈的鹰嘴豆是我吃过的最好的
Your mother's chickpeas are the best I've ever eaten

804
01:21:04,910 --> 01:21:06,040
周四见？
See you on Thursday?

805
01:21:06,250 --> 01:21:07,910
周四？可能
Thursday? Maybe

806
01:21:08,120 --> 01:21:11,540
如果罗莎还没回来 现在不会太久了
If Rosa hasn't come back yet. It can't be long now

807
01:21:13,790 --> 01:21:16,080
不管怎样 你都可以来
Well, you can come anyway

808
01:21:16,370 --> 01:21:18,660
你将如何向她解释？
And how will you explain it to her?

809
01:21:20,500 --> 01:21:21,540
我不知道
I don't know

810
01:21:22,660 --> 01:21:25,870
以防万一 我会说再见 好吗？再见 伊吉尼奥
Just in case, I'll say goodbye, okay? Bye, Higinio

811
01:21:28,000 --> 01:21:29,120
再见 恩里克
Bye, Enrique

812
01:21:31,120 --> 01:21:32,540
小心你出去的路
Careful on your way out

813
01:21:33,000 --> 01:21:34,290
别担心
Don't worry

814
01:22:04,290 --> 01:22:05,290
伊吉尼奥
Higinio

815
01:22:44,500 --> 01:22:45,950
你好吗？-好吧
How are you? - Fine

816
01:22:46,290 --> 01:22:48,540
你呢？-让我看看
What about you? - Let me take a look

817
01:22:51,330 --> 01:22:52,620
你看起来棒极了
You look great

818
01:22:53,120 --> 01:22:55,370
比我期望的更好找到你
Better than I expected to find you

819
01:23:10,620 --> 01:23:11,950
是个男孩
It's a boy

820
01:23:20,870 --> 01:23:22,250
来这里
Come here

821
01:23:26,450 --> 01:23:28,250
哦 我的小家伙
Oh, my little one

822
01:23:37,790 --> 01:23:38,950
你看到了吗？
Did you see?

823
01:23:39,290 --> 01:23:40,290
打招呼
Say hello

824
01:23:42,000 --> 01:23:43,790
见过他有多小吗？
Seen how little he is?

825
01:23:44,250 --> 01:23:46,750
没那么小 他差不多重5公斤
Not that little, he weighed almost 5kg

826
01:23:47,200 --> 01:23:50,290
医生说他一生中从未见过这样的事情
The doctor said he'd never seen anything like it in his life

827
01:23:56,040 --> 01:23:57,910
我们会有麻烦的
We're going to have a problem

828
01:23:59,370 --> 01:24:00,950
他看起来和你一样
He looks just like you

829
01:24:02,410 --> 01:24:03,500
什么事？
Yes?

830
01:24:04,450 --> 01:24:06,540
你知道他们会在村子里说什么吗？
You know what they'll say in the village?

831
01:24:08,120 --> 01:24:09,370
就像我一样
Just like me

832
01:24:10,330 --> 01:24:11,870
是的 现在
Yes, for now

833
01:24:18,950 --> 01:24:20,950
他还不认识你
He doesn't know you yet

834
01:24:21,370 --> 01:24:22,950
那里 那里 亲爱的
There, there, sweetie

835
01:24:34,370 --> 01:24:37,500
今天标志着盟军在欧洲的胜利
Today marks the Allied victory in Europe

836
01:24:37,750 --> 01:24:40,120
德国已经无条件投降
Germany has surrendered unconditionally

837
01:24:40,330 --> 01:24:42,370
欧洲的战争结束了
War is over in Europe

838
01:24:42,790 --> 01:24:46,450
投降仪式于凌晨2点41分在兰斯签署
The surrender was signed in Reims at 2.41am

839
01:24:47,040 --> 01:24:48,290
联合通讯社
The United Press agency

840
01:24:48,370 --> 01:24:51,790
宣布德国外交部长冯·克罗西克
announces that the German foreign minister, von Krosigk,

841
01:24:52,000 --> 01:24:53,950
弗伦斯堡的广播
broadcasting from Flensburg,

842
01:24:54,000 --> 01:24:57,290
声明最高统帅部接受无条件投降
states that the high command accepts unconditional surrender

843
01:24:57,870 --> 01:25:01,290
该机构补充说 官方的胜利宣言
The same agency adds that the official declaration of victory

844
01:25:01,410 --> 01:25:03,290
将在下午6点制作
will be made at 6pm

845
01:25:03,370 --> 01:25:04,950
这将会结束
This is going to end

846
01:25:05,080 --> 01:25:08,000
我们可以出去了 -他正要睡觉
We'll be able to go outside. - He was just going to sleep

847
01:25:08,200 --> 01:25:10,500
没关系 我们要庆祝
It doesn't matter, we have to celebrate

848
01:25:10,750 --> 01:25:13,040
我会给你你应得的生活
that I'm going to give you the life you deserve

849
01:25:13,250 --> 01:25:14,950
现在 詹姆 杰米
Right now, Jaime. Jaime

850
01:25:15,120 --> 01:25:16,950
把他给我 -现在 现在
Give him to me. - Right now, right now

851
01:25:17,080 --> 01:25:20,000
和爸爸一起 现在爸爸在街上
With Daddy. Right now with Daddy on the street

852
01:25:34,660 --> 01:25:35,790
詹姆
Jaime!

853
01:25:38,000 --> 01:25:39,080
詹姆
Jaime!

854
01:25:39,950 --> 01:25:41,040
你在做什么?
What are you doing?

855
01:25:41,250 --> 01:25:43,290
去散步 来吗？
Going to the promenade, coming?

856
01:25:44,120 --> 01:25:46,290
安东尼奥能和我们一起去吗？
Can Antonio come with us?

857
01:25:46,870 --> 01:25:48,500
我们有很多人
There are a lot of us

858
01:25:48,910 --> 01:25:50,290
只是看看 然后
Just to look, then

859
01:25:50,500 --> 01:25:51,500
行
Okay

860
01:25:51,620 --> 01:25:52,620
走吧
Let's go

861
01:26:01,200 --> 01:26:06,410
十年-十年的时期
decade - period of ten years

862
01:26:09,450 --> 01:26:13,790
又来了？帮我个忙 把事情了结 我以前告诉过你
Again? Do me a favour and close things. I've told you before

863
01:26:14,200 --> 01:26:15,660
好了
Done

864
01:26:16,620 --> 01:26:18,620
西班牙已经加入了联合国
Spain has joined the UN

865
01:26:19,000 --> 01:26:20,290
那是什么？
What's that?

866
01:26:20,450 --> 01:26:25,040
联合起来和平解决问题的一组国家
A group of nations that joined together to solve things peacefully

867
01:26:25,250 --> 01:26:27,620
他们知道佛朗哥在这里做什么吗？
Do they know what Franco is doing here?

868
01:26:27,790 --> 01:26:31,000
不知道 但是现在我们是联合国的一员了
No idea. But now we're a member of the UN

869
01:26:31,750 --> 01:26:33,910
小心 这很热
Watch out, this is hot

870
01:26:35,580 --> 01:26:39,250
詹姆 今天早上和你在一起的那个孩子是谁？
Who's that kid you were with this morning, Jaime?

871
01:26:39,580 --> 01:26:40,830
拉法
Rafa

872
01:26:44,160 --> 01:26:45,660
你去哪了？
Where did you go?

873
01:26:46,120 --> 01:26:47,750
踢足球
To play football

874
01:26:48,540 --> 01:26:52,200
去那个我告诉过你适合玩耍的荒地？
To that waste ground where I told you it was good for playing?

875
01:26:55,830 --> 01:26:56,870
谁玩的？
And who played?

876
01:26:58,000 --> 01:26:59,620
很多你不认识的孩子
Lots of kids you don't know

877
01:26:59,750 --> 01:27:02,410
如果你告诉我他们是谁 我会的
If you tell me who they are I will

878
01:27:02,620 --> 01:27:04,000
我不知道他们的名字
I don't know their names

879
01:27:04,120 --> 01:27:06,450
嗯 你必须给他们起个名字
Well, you must call them something

880
01:27:06,660 --> 01:27:09,120
汤姆 迪克 哈利 把球递给我 好吗？
Tom, Dick, Harry, pass me the ball, right?

881
01:27:09,250 --> 01:27:11,790
我们不太在意名字
We're not much bothered about names

882
01:27:11,950 --> 01:27:14,290
我说:嘿 传球 就这样
I say: hey, pass it! That's it

883
01:27:14,750 --> 01:27:16,580
坐进去 等等 等等
Sit in. Hang on, wait

884
01:27:17,330 --> 01:27:18,580
就这样
That's it

885
01:27:19,000 --> 01:27:20,040
这边请
There you go

886
01:27:22,160 --> 01:27:23,160
这里
Here

887
01:27:24,790 --> 01:27:26,790
村子里发生了什么事？
What's going on in the village?

888
01:27:29,290 --> 01:27:31,290
生活 伊吉尼奥 我不知道
Life, Higinio, I don't know

889
01:27:33,750 --> 01:27:35,910
一定发生了什么事 嗯？
Something must be going on, huh?

890
01:27:36,950 --> 01:27:39,750
他们昨天撞倒了普鲁登的狗
They ran over Pruden's dog yesterday

891
01:27:40,950 --> 01:27:42,870
邮差恩里克要结婚了
Enrique the postman is getting married

892
01:27:43,540 --> 01:27:45,040
他要结婚了？
He's getting married?

893
01:27:46,790 --> 01:27:51,080
每个人都认为他会保持单身 但不 他要结婚了
Everyone thought he'd stay a bachelor, but no, he's marrying

894
01:27:58,200 --> 01:28:01,830
请停下来 詹姆 我不能集中精神
Stop that please, Jaime, I can't concentrate

895
01:28:05,200 --> 01:28:07,080
你为什么穿女人的羊毛衫？
Why are you wearing a woman's cardigan?

896
01:28:07,200 --> 01:28:08,910
你不喜欢吗？
Don't you like it?

897
01:28:09,040 --> 01:28:10,370
我不知道
I don't know

898
01:28:11,000 --> 01:28:13,910
你知道你要做什么 -什么？
You know what you have to do. - What?

899
01:28:15,410 --> 01:28:16,450
成长
Grow up

900
01:28:16,910 --> 01:28:18,080
行
Okay

901
01:28:19,750 --> 01:28:21,290
我去拿
I'll get it

902
01:28:25,450 --> 01:28:27,040
闭嘴
Shut that

903
01:28:32,160 --> 01:28:33,160
闭嘴 好吗？
Shut it, will you?

904
01:28:33,250 --> 01:28:34,370
你阿姨在吗？
Is your aunt there?

905
01:28:34,580 --> 01:28:35,660
不 她出去了
No, she went out

906
01:28:35,830 --> 01:28:38,000
这条裤子需要缝补
These trousers need mending

907
01:28:38,160 --> 01:28:41,830
你可以把它们留在这里 我会记下来的 进来
You can leave them here, I'll make a note. Come in

908
01:28:43,950 --> 01:28:46,000
你叫什么名字？你需要什么？
What's your name? What do you need?

909
01:28:46,410 --> 01:28:48,450
你不觉得这有点年轻吗？
Aren't you a bit young for this?

910
01:28:50,160 --> 01:28:52,660
不知道 我已经做过一千次了
Dunno. I've done it a thousand times

911
01:28:52,830 --> 01:28:53,910
是吗？
Yeah?

912
01:28:54,950 --> 01:28:56,540
好吧 写下来
All right, write this down

913
01:29:00,370 --> 01:29:01,370
就这样
That's it

914
01:29:01,660 --> 01:29:04,290
我叫贡萨洛·帕拉西奥
My name is Gonzalo Palacio

915
01:29:07,330 --> 01:29:08,410
好吧 -看
Okay. - Look

916
01:29:08,620 --> 01:29:10,750
拉链需要修理 看
The zip needs fixing, look

917
01:29:11,080 --> 01:29:13,410
它需要改变 我不知道
It needs changing, I don't know

918
01:29:13,620 --> 01:29:15,950
然后 这个洞 看
And then, this hole here. Look

919
01:29:19,120 --> 01:29:20,250
好吗？
Okay?

920
01:29:22,410 --> 01:29:23,870
怎么了？
So, what's up?

921
01:29:25,080 --> 01:29:28,000
你是家里的男人 对吗？
You're the man of the house, right?

922
01:29:29,410 --> 01:29:30,410
是
Yeah

923
01:29:30,700 --> 01:29:32,700
你阿姨对你好吗？
Is your aunt good to you?

924
01:29:37,120 --> 01:29:40,330
你知道你叔叔和婶婶是我的邻居吗？
You know that your aunt and uncle were neighbors of mine?

925
01:29:41,330 --> 01:29:42,660
他们对我很严厉
They were tough on me

926
01:29:49,250 --> 01:29:51,910
你想念他们吗？
And do you miss them?

927
01:29:52,250 --> 01:29:53,450
谁？
Who?

928
01:29:54,000 --> 01:29:56,870
你认为是谁？你妈妈和爸爸
Who do you think? Your mum and dad

929
01:29:57,660 --> 01:30:00,000
是的 是的 当然
Yeah. Yeah, of course

930
01:30:02,660 --> 01:30:03,910
怎么了？
What's up?

931
01:30:04,250 --> 01:30:05,750
你不确定吗？
Are you unsure?

932
01:30:06,580 --> 01:30:07,830
不
No

933
01:30:09,040 --> 01:30:10,160
我不是不确定
I'm not unsure

934
01:30:11,000 --> 01:30:13,910
你不记得了 你还小 是吗？
You wouldn't remember, you were little, weren't you?

935
01:30:16,620 --> 01:30:18,410
那只猫有你的舌头吗？
Has the cat got your tongue?

936
01:30:20,290 --> 01:30:21,410
我不咬人 小伙子
I don't bite, lad

937
01:30:23,000 --> 01:30:23,830
你好 贡萨洛
Hello, Gonzalo

938
01:30:23,950 --> 01:30:25,410
下午好 -怎么了？
Afternoon. - What's up?

939
01:30:25,620 --> 01:30:30,160
我带了这条裤子给你补 他正在记笔记
I brought these trousers for you to mend and he was taking note

940
01:30:30,700 --> 01:30:32,250
让我们看看
Let's have a look

941
01:30:33,080 --> 01:30:34,540
好吧 那么
Okay, then

942
01:30:34,700 --> 01:30:37,620
我将在两天内准备好这个
I'll have this ready in two days

943
01:30:38,290 --> 01:30:40,160
两天后？-你可以捡起来
In two days? - You can pick it up

944
01:30:40,330 --> 01:30:42,950
我妻子可能会来
My wife might come by

945
01:30:43,120 --> 01:30:46,700
好吧 那再见 -好吧 再见 小伙子
All right. Bye, then. - Okay. Bye, lad

946
01:30:47,700 --> 01:30:48,330
再见
Bye

947
01:30:48,540 --> 01:30:49,950
再见 罗莎 -再见
Bye, Rosa. - Bye

948
01:30:51,950 --> 01:30:54,370
他在这里做什么？为什么出乎意料？
What's he doing here? Why out of the blue?

949
01:30:54,450 --> 01:30:57,000
不知道 -你没看见他在附近吗？
No idea. - Don't you see him around?

950
01:30:57,160 --> 01:30:58,830
有时候 -多久一次？
Sometimes. - How often?

951
01:30:58,950 --> 01:31:00,410
这个村庄没那么大
The village isn't that big

952
01:31:00,540 --> 01:31:02,040
让我们考虑一下
Let's think about it

953
01:31:02,120 --> 01:31:04,910
他一定说了什么 暗示了什么
He must have said something, hinted at something

954
01:31:05,040 --> 01:31:06,580
他带着裤子来了
He came with the trousers

955
01:31:06,750 --> 01:31:10,950
他来是为了让你能修补它们和其他东西 是吗？
He came so you could mend them and something else, huh?

956
01:31:11,700 --> 01:31:13,700
我跟你说了什么？
And what did I tell you?

957
01:31:14,200 --> 01:31:16,080
我们排练了多少次了？
How many times have we rehearsed it?

958
