我不能
I can't

1012
01:38:17,410 --> 01:38:19,200
规矩点 嗯？
And behave yourself, huh?

1013
01:38:19,370 --> 01:38:21,000
是的 别担心 阿姨
Yes, don't worry, Auntie

1014
01:39:15,910 --> 01:39:17,080
我能拿我的手提包吗？
Can I have my handbag?

1015
01:39:17,290 --> 01:39:20,330
请问这是谁的电话号码？
Whose phone number is this, please?

1016
01:39:20,950 --> 01:39:23,450
一定是顾客的 我不记得了
Must be a customer's, I don't remember

1017
01:39:23,620 --> 01:39:25,080
你什么时候开始抽烟了？
Since when do you smoke?

1018
01:39:25,200 --> 01:39:26,200
我不知道
I don't

1019
01:39:29,120 --> 01:39:32,790
你为什么在这里翻找？-弄清楚你对我隐瞒了什么
Why are you rummaging here? - Figuring out what you keep from me

1020
01:39:32,950 --> 01:39:34,790
正是我所需要的
Just what I needed

1021
01:39:34,950 --> 01:39:38,080
你什么时候开始和国民警卫队的妻子混在一起了？
Since when do you mix with the civil guard's wife?

1022
01:39:39,830 --> 01:39:41,200
哪个国民警卫队？
Which civil guard?

1023
01:39:41,370 --> 01:39:43,950
你可以躺在那里 而不是在家
You can lie out there, not here at home

1024
01:39:44,080 --> 01:39:46,580
你什么时候开始和她混在一起了？
Since when do you mix with her?

1025
01:39:48,950 --> 01:39:51,200
我不知道在哪里...-我看见你了
I don't know where... - I saw you

1026
01:39:51,410 --> 01:39:53,250
别大惊小怪的 好吗？
Don't kick up a fuss, okay?

1027
01:39:53,410 --> 01:39:57,580
和她交往了15年 你却不告诉我？
Fifteen years hanging out with her and you're not going to tell me?

1028
01:39:58,120 --> 01:40:02,580
不是十五年 事情不会一夜之间发生
Not fifteen years, things don't happen overnight

1029
01:40:02,750 --> 01:40:05,870
看在上帝的份上 罗莎
For God's sake, Rosa

1030
01:40:06,370 --> 01:40:08,120
看在上帝份上
For God's sake

1031
01:40:08,370 --> 01:40:10,700
你知道你在做什么吗？
Do you realise what you're doing?

1032
01:40:11,040 --> 01:40:12,910
你正在危及一切
You're jeopardising everything

1033
01:40:13,040 --> 01:40:14,830
我该怎么办？-为什么是她？
What should I do? - Why her?

1034
01:40:14,950 --> 01:40:16,700
解释什么...-你解释
Explain what... - You explain

1035
01:40:16,870 --> 01:40:20,080
如果她在街上拦住我想聊天 怎么办？
If she stops me on the street and wants to chat, what?

1036
01:40:20,250 --> 01:40:23,370
我说不吗？-这会减轻你的良心吗？
Do I say no? - Does it ease your conscience?

1037
01:40:23,540 --> 01:40:26,200
我是睡在尸体上的人
I'm the one who sleeps on top of the dead body

1038
01:40:26,950 --> 01:40:28,250
拜托 罗莎
Please, Rosa

1039
01:40:28,540 --> 01:40:30,540
你为什么不出去？
Why don't you go outside?

1040
01:40:30,750 --> 01:40:32,330
你可以做你自己
You can be yourself

1041
01:40:32,540 --> 01:40:34,250
出去吧 -什么？
Go on out. - What?

1042
01:40:34,330 --> 01:40:37,080
这里有一个罗莎 外面还有一个
There's one Rosa here and another out there

1043
01:40:37,160 --> 01:40:39,000
你是个骗子 我不认识你
You're an impostor. I don't know you

1044
01:40:39,160 --> 01:40:40,330
当然不
Of course not

1045
01:40:40,580 --> 01:40:41,870
我能怎么做呢？
What can I do?

1046
01:40:41,950 --> 01:40:46,290
呆在这里？和你一起爬进去 没有生活？
Stay here? Crawl in there with you, not have a life?

1047
01:40:46,370 --> 01:40:48,160
我是你丈夫
I'm your husband

1048
01:40:48,750 --> 01:40:51,250
我受够了 希吉尼奥 -什么？
I'm sick of it, Higinio. - Of what?

1049
01:40:51,540 --> 01:40:53,950
你讨厌什么？-什么？
What are you sick of? - What?

1050
01:40:54,000 --> 01:40:56,040
被关起来？那是我
Of being cooped up? That's me

1051
01:40:56,120 --> 01:40:58,450
厌倦了这样的生活 我受不了了
Sick of living this way, I can't take it

1052
01:40:58,750 --> 01:41:01,700
厌倦了对街上的每个人撒谎
Sick of lying to everyone on the street

1053
01:41:01,790 --> 01:41:05,580
我呢？我看不到阳光 关了二十年
And me? I don't see the light of day. Twenty years cooped up

1054
01:41:05,660 --> 01:41:08,540
我的一生都是你和一个可能不属于我的孩子
My whole life is you and a kid who might not be mine

1055
