再说一遍
Say that again

1056
01:41:14,080 --> 01:41:15,200
这是你的主意
It was your idea

1057
01:41:16,120 --> 01:41:18,000
这是你的主意 你的主意
It was your idea, your idea

1058
01:41:18,160 --> 01:41:21,660
你对我说...-重复你刚才说的话
You said to me... - Repeat what you just said

1059
01:41:21,830 --> 01:41:24,950
你说我儿子的事 -你说 呆在那里
What you said about my son. - You said, stay in there

1060
01:41:25,160 --> 01:41:26,910
你把我关了20年
You locked me up for 20 years

1061
01:41:26,950 --> 01:41:28,160
有一个快速的解决方案
There's a quick solution

1062
01:41:28,330 --> 01:41:30,120
被锁在那个破洞里
Locked up in that shitty hole

1063
01:41:30,290 --> 01:41:32,290
那我来为你开门
I'll open the door for you, then

1064
01:41:32,450 --> 01:41:33,910
住手 -不 出去
Stop it. - No, get out

1065
01:41:33,950 --> 01:41:35,950
走吧 我再也受不了你了 -罗莎
Go, I can't stand you anymore! - Rosa

1066
01:41:36,040 --> 01:41:38,790
我再也受不了你了
I can't stand you anymore

1067
01:41:45,950 --> 01:41:48,870
你甚至不能出去
You're not even capable of going out

1068
01:41:48,950 --> 01:41:51,870
你做不到 那是你的问题
You can't do it, that's your problem

1069
01:41:53,790 --> 01:41:55,370
好 好 好
Well, well, well

1070
01:41:57,370 --> 01:42:00,700
我们这么做是为了能在一起 对吗？
We did all of this so we could be together, right?

1071
01:42:02,000 --> 01:42:04,080
看看我们在一起有多好
Well look how together we are

1072
01:42:06,870 --> 01:42:09,910
你弄坏了我的东西
You've broken my things

1073
01:42:42,250 --> 01:42:43,620
你什么时候到的？
When did you arrive?

1074
01:42:43,700 --> 01:42:44,700
昨晚
Last night

1075
01:42:45,910 --> 01:42:48,870
他迟到了 这就是为什么我没有告诉你
He got in late. That's why I didn't tell you

1076
01:42:50,660 --> 01:42:52,370
他告诉我大海是什么样的
He told me what the sea is like

1077
01:42:52,540 --> 01:42:54,870
告诉你爸爸 -是的
Tell your dad. - Yeah

1078
01:42:55,250 --> 01:42:57,250
我告诉她它是咸的
I was telling her that it's salty

1079
01:42:57,410 --> 01:43:00,040
但不像你在里面放了盐
But not like you've added salt to it

1080
01:43:00,580 --> 01:43:02,370
一个波浪打在我的脸上
A wave hit me in the face,

1081
01:43:02,580 --> 01:43:07,160
它闻起来像新鲜的鱼或者类似的东西
and it smelled like fresh fish or something like that

1082
01:43:07,580 --> 01:43:09,660
温度会变化
And the temperature changes

1083
01:43:09,910 --> 01:43:13,580
突然 你感觉到一股寒流围绕着你的双腿
Suddenly you feel a cold current around your legs

1084
01:43:14,450 --> 01:43:17,660
你呆在同一个地方 但还有另一层温暖
You stay in the same place, but there's another warm layer

1085
01:43:19,000 --> 01:43:20,620
听起来不错
Sounds nice

1086
01:43:21,410 --> 01:43:25,040
海底很奇怪 就像陆地一样 但是
And the seabed is strange, it's like the land but

1087
01:43:25,370 --> 01:43:27,660
全是沙子
it's all sand

1088
