它是什么颜色的？
What colour is it?

1089
01:43:31,330 --> 01:43:32,620
深蓝
Dark blue

1090
01:43:32,910 --> 01:43:36,000
在其他地方它看起来是绿色的
And it looks greenish in other places

1091
01:43:36,410 --> 01:43:39,250
好像它在动 蓝色是
As if it were moving. The blue is

