SPAIN - 40 BILLION IN REVENUE SUNSHINE BOOM

1096
01:44:19,700 --> 01:44:22,830
乐观地面对1963年
FACING 1963 WITH OPTIMISM

1097
01:44:28,700 --> 01:44:30,910
今天 像昨天一样
Today, like yesterday

1098
