亲爱的听众
Dear listeners

1099
01:44:37,580 --> 01:44:40,450
出来一会儿 你被关了一整天
Come out for a bit. You've been cooped up all day

1100
01:44:40,660 --> 01:44:42,250
我在这里很好
I'm fine here

1101
01:44:43,080 --> 01:44:44,700
想要点什么吗？
Want something?

1102
01:44:44,950 --> 01:44:46,870
嗨 我和一个朋友在这里
Hi. I'm here with a friend

1103
01:44:47,040 --> 01:44:48,580
在这里等我
Wait for me here

1104
01:44:52,330 --> 01:44:54,080
嗨 -嗨 妈妈
Hi. - Hi, Mum

1105
01:44:54,410 --> 01:44:55,830
过来 胡安
Come here, Juan

1106
01:44:56,830 --> 01:45:00,370
爸爸 不用担心 胡安知道你在这里
Dad, no need to worry, Juan knows you're here

1107
01:45:00,870 --> 01:45:04,870
对不起 我之前不能让你知道 但是他有麻烦 需要帮助
Sorry I couldn't let you know before, but he's in a fix and needs help

1108
01:45:05,250 --> 01:45:06,250
罗莎 我妈妈
Rosa, my mum

1109
01:45:06,410 --> 01:45:07,450
见到你很高兴
Pleased to meet you

1110
01:45:07,620 --> 01:45:10,950
25年来一直保守着我在这里的秘密
Twenty-five years keeping it a secret that I'm here,

1111
01:45:11,080 --> 01:45:13,450
现在因为你认为事情正在改变
and now because you think things are changing,

1112
01:45:13,620 --> 01:45:16,370
你告诉一个朋友你爸爸藏在这里？
you tell a friend your dad is hiding here?

1113
01:45:16,660 --> 01:45:18,910
只是几天而已
It's only for a couple of days

1114
01:45:19,200 --> 01:45:21,330
你不能表现出一些团结吗？
Can't you show some solidarity?

1115
01:45:21,620 --> 01:45:23,790
你的战斗精神呢？
What about your fighting spirit?

1116
01:45:35,950 --> 01:45:39,660
他们在塞戈维亚找到了一个躲了20年的人
They found a guy in Segovia, 20 years in hiding

1117
01:45:40,290 --> 01:45:42,200
他们得到了线报
They got a tip-off

1118
01:45:43,790 --> 01:45:46,870
他们说马德里没有一个特别的小组来寻找你的同类
They say Madrid has not a special group to find your kind

1119
01:45:46,950 --> 01:45:50,830
当局查明是否有当地的密报或线索
The authorities find out if there are local tip-offs or clues

1120
01:45:50,950 --> 01:45:54,620
马德里没有具体的搜索行动
There's no specific search operation organised from Madrid

1121
01:45:54,790 --> 01:45:56,450
你就像一个老师
You're like a teacher

1122
01:45:57,080 --> 01:45:58,080
谢谢
Thanks

1123
01:45:58,250 --> 01:45:59,790
这不是恭维
It's not a compliment

1124
01:46:12,870 --> 01:46:13,870
什么事？
Yes?

1125
01:46:14,330 --> 01:46:18,080
她说我越来越执迷不悟 不肯给我信息
She says I'm getting obsessive, won't give me information

1126
01:46:19,000 --> 01:46:20,200
他们警告过你吗？
Did they warn you?

1127
01:46:20,950 --> 01:46:22,250
没有 只是轻声说
No, just said speak softly

1128
01:46:24,120 --> 01:46:27,200
你说你看到了另一个人的藏身之处
You said you saw the other guy's hiding place

1129
01:46:28,410 --> 01:46:30,700
是的 但是当他不在的时候
Yeah, but when he wasn't there

1130
01:46:32,330 --> 01:46:33,580
给我细节
Give me details

1131
01:46:34,580 --> 01:46:37,080
他是一个在前线战斗的无政府主义者
He was an anarchist who fought on the front

1132
01:46:37,160 --> 01:46:39,410
不 我是说藏身之处
No, I mean the hiding place

1133
01:46:42,540 --> 01:46:44,910
在一段楼梯下
Under a flight of stairs

1134
01:46:45,250 --> 01:46:47,620
他建了一堵墙来盖住那个洞
He built a wall to cover the hole

1135
01:46:52,950 --> 01:46:55,700
如果这是在楼梯下面
If this was under the stairs

1136
